### URL 단축 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/api/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://www.google.com"
}


### URL 단축 등록 — 만료시간 포함
POST http://localhost:8080/api/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://www.github.com",
    "expiresAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z"
}


### URL 단축 등록 — 클릭 횟수 제한
POST http://localhost:8080/api/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "url": "https://www.naver.com",
    "clickLimit": 5
}


### URL 단축 등록 — url 없이 보내기
POST http://localhost:8080/api/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{}



### 리다이렉트
GET http://localhost:8080/HhSoVOC


### [Worker 전용 resolve
GET http://localhost:8080/api/resolve/HhSoVOC


### Worker 헬스체크
GET http://localhost:8787/health


### Worker 경유 리다이렉트
GET http://localhost:8787/HhSoVOC


### Worker 경유 — shortCode 없이 루트 접근
GET http://localhost:8787/